>\n\n==Early life and career==\nRich was born in Harlem NY, raised in Lowell, Massachusetts. He created success for himself as a producer by moving to Los Angeles in 2018 after graduating school as an audio engineer. Rich is also known for executive producing Cousin Stizz's debut album \"Trying To Find My Next Thrill.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://genius.com/artists/Lil-rich|last1=Nostro|first1=Lauren|title=Lil Rich Lyrics, Songs & Albums|website=Genius|access-date=22 April 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://djbooth.net/features/2019-09-12-lil-rich-cousin-stizz-executive-producer-interview|title=Lil Rich Breaks Down His Role As Executive Producer|last1=Chesman|first1=Donna-Claire|website=DJ Booth|accessdate=22 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Production credits==\nSelected production discography of Lil Rich<ref>{{cite web |title=Lil Rich |url=https://www.discogs.com/artist/4571720-Lil-Rich-3 |website=Discogs |accessdate=23 April 2020}}</ref>\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+\n!Year\n!Title \n!Artist(s)\n!Album\n!Credits\n|-\n|rowspan=\"6\" |2020\n|\"Covergirl\"\n|BIA\n| rowspan=\"2\" |''Rich Tiers''\n| rowspan=\"6\" |Producer\n|-\n|\"Free BIA (1st Day Out)\"\n|BIA\n|-\n|\"Nothing To Lose\"\n|Black Fortune\n|''Nothing To Lose - Single''\n|-\n|\"Givin' Body\"\n|Donmonique\n|''Givin' Body - Single''\n|-\n|\"Savage (Featuring G Perico)\"\n|Rob Stone\n|''Savage - Single''\n|-\n|\"Perfect [Remix] (Featuring BIA & Doja Cat)\"\n|Cousin Stizz\n|''Perfect [Remix] - Single''\n|-\n|rowspan=\"8\" |2019\n|\"Perfect (Featuring City Girls)\n|Cousin Stizz\n| rowspan=\"7\" |''Trying To Find My Next Thrill''\n| rowspan=\"8\" |Producer\n|-\n|\"Jump Out The Phone (Featuring Leven Kali)\"\n|Cousin Stizz\n|-\n|\"Toast 2 That (Featuring Freddie Gibbs)\"\n|Cousin Stizz\n|-\n|\"Off With Ya Head\"\n|Cousin Stizz  \n|-\n|\"Meds\"\n|Cousin Stizz \n|- \n|\"What U Bout\"\n|Cousin Stizz \n|- \n|\"SOSO (Featuring $ean Wire)\"\n|Cousin Stizz \n|- \n|\"Hard Bottoms & White Socks\"\n|YG\n|''4REAL 4REAL''\n|-\n|row